Name: RRRR3
About the game: The events of the game take place in 3020, after the events of the RRRR and RRRR2 games, the super-soldier Rabbit finds the last hope for saving the soldier's super duper Fish and awakens from cryogenic freezing. Soldier Pisces has a dangerous journey in a world full of dangers and deadly traps. Explore the world of the game, solve puzzles, fight alien opponents and dangerous robots. Features Explore locations with various traps. Fight against opponents. Open doors and mechanisms. Many funny elements and references to popular heroes.
